queries: A vulgar or crude sign for many signers.
oldentry: Popular explanation: the head of a baby emerging from the body.
verblex: 1. Of human babies or the young of many different types of animals, to come out of the body of one's mother. English = (be) born.
2. Of women or the females of many different types of animals, to produce a baby from your body. English = give birth.
nomlex: 1. The act of a baby emerging from the body of its mother. English = birth.
